.row
  .col-xs-12.col-sm-8
    %h1 Thank you for your donation!
    %p Completely impact multifunctional processes and wireless supply chains. Dynamically engage business.

    .well
      .row
        .col-xs-8
          %h3 #{@donation.type} to AdoptTogether
          %p for #{@family.full_name}’s Adoption
        .col-xs-4
          %span.pull-right= pretty_dollars(@donation.amount)
        .col-xs-8
          %p Tip for AdoptTogether
        .col-xs-4
          %span.pull-right= pretty_dollars(@donation.tip_total)
      %hr
      .row
        .col-xs-8
          %p Total
        .col-xs-4
          %span.pull-right #{pretty_dollars(@donation.total_amount_in_dollars)}
    .small.help-block A receipt with this information has just been emailed to you.

    %h2 Take it to the next level: Help them reach their goal. There are 2 more ways to help:
    %div(class="fb-share-button" data-href="#{family_url(@family)}" data-layout="box_count")
    %a(href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-url="#{family_url(@family)}" data-text="I just donated towards #{@family.full_name}'s adoption on @adoptt, you should too!" data-count="vertical")Tweet
    :javascript
      !function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],p=/^http:/.test(d.location)?'http':'https';if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src=p+'://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js';fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document, 'script', 'twitter-wjs');
    <script src="https://apis.google.com/js/platform.js" async defer></script>
    <g:plusone size="tall" data-annotation="vertical-bubble" data-href="#{family_url(@family)}" data-size="tall"></g:plusone>
    <script src="//platform.linkedin.com/in.js" type="text/javascript"> lang: en_US</script>
    <script type="IN/Share" data-counter="top"></script>
    <a href="//www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=#{Rack::Utils.escape(family_url(@family))}&media=#{Rack::Utils.escape(@family.photo.large.url)}&description=Next%20stop%3A%20Pinterest" data-pin-do="buttonPin" data-pin-config="above" data-pin-color="red" data-pin-height="28"><img src="//assets.pinterest.com/images/pidgets/pinit_fg_en_rect_red_28.png" /></a>
    <!-- Please call pinit.js only once per page -->
    <script type="text/javascript" async defer src="//assets.pinterest.com/js/pinit.js"></script>
    =text_field_tag :url, family_url(@family), class: "form-control", onClick: "this.setSelectionRange(0, this.value.length)"
    %h2 Raise Money for this adoption from your Friends & Family
    %p A small river named Duden flows by their place and supplies it with the necessary regelialia. It is a paraismatic country, in which roasted parts of sentences fly into your mouth.
    %a.btn.btn-primary Start a Fundraiser for this Family
  %aside.col-xs-12.col-sm-4
    %h2 You donated to
    = render 'shared/family_thumb', :family => @family
    %h2 FAQ
    %h3 Are my donations tax deductible?
    %p Yes! Your donation is going to the Hoping Hearts foundation and then it is being appropriated to the families.
    %h3 Can I send a check?
    %p Of course! Just make your check payable to AdoptTogether and put the family’s name on the envelope & in the memo and mail it to:
    %p
      AdoptTogether
      %br
      251 W. Central Ave. #278
      %br
      Springboro, OH 45066
      %br
      1 (888) 826-0948
    %h3 Can I give a monthly contribution?
    %p Yes, on the last step we’ll ask if you want to make this a monthly contribution.
    %h3 Can I edit or cancel my monthly contribution?
    %p You can view or edit your monthly contribution at any time here.
